      <title>坦桑尼亚禁止计划举行的集会后释放反对派领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/tanzania-frees-opposition-leaders-it-detained-to-prevent-unrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[坦桑尼亚释放了 520 名被拘留的反对派成员，以阻止他们举行青年集会，当局称这可能引发骚乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/tanzania-frees-opposition-leaders-it-detained-to-prevent-unrest</guid>
