    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯袭击导致乌克兰库尔斯克附近地区电力供应中断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/russian-strikes-cut-power-supply-in-ukrainian-region-near-kursk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯导弹袭击连夜中断了乌克兰北部库尔斯克地区附近苏梅市部分市区的电力和天然气供应。由于乌克兰突然越境入侵，该地区一直处于战乱之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/russian-strikes-cut-power-supply-in-ukrainian-region-near-kursk</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 06:26:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
