    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国释放更多台湾渔船渔民 彰显进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/china-frees-more-fishermen-from-taiwan-boats-in-sign-of-progress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国在一周内第二次释放了在台湾渔船上被扣押的渔民，这表明尽管中台关系存在根本分歧，但双方能够解决一些小问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/china-frees-more-fishermen-from-taiwan-boats-in-sign-of-progress</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 04:19:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
